data.description: GREAT PRICE! What a deal for under $400K. Come see this lovely Home in highly desired Lewisburg neighborhood, on 1.05 Acres. Enjoy the Beautiful Park Like Setting back yard, Remodeled Kitchen with Quartz countertops, Custom “soft-close” Cabinets, New Dishwasher & Beverage Fridge. With a Recently added 4th Bedroom. Just added New Tile in Upstairs Bath, New Live Strand Bamboo throughout downstairs Living area, Master Down with En Suite, All New Carpet upstairs, Fireplace in LR, Screened Porch w/roll up privacy screens, HVAC 2/years, Easy Access Walk-In Attic Storage, 2-Car Garage. *NO HOA*
